    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable, stylish ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-cared for, runs super smoothly, and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
