      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor surface imperfections consistent with careful road use. Inside, you will find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring premium leather upholstery that remains supple and supportive. Every electronic feature\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it boasts a documented history of consistent servicing, including a recent professional inspection and fluid flush, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience. It is a sophisticated, turn-key choice for a buyer who values reliability and comfort.",
      "price": 38500.0,
